<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8334420>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Amalosia saxicola sp. nov. in life: (A, B) Magnetic Island; (C) Scawfell Island; (D) Massey Ck, Eungella. Photos: Conrad Hoskin." ;
