<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8334424>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Adult A. saxicola sp. nov. QM J32775 (Brandy Ck, near Airlie Beach) compared with adult A. queenslandia sp. nov. QM J97599 (Mt Spurgeon). Note the more robust form of A. saxicola sp. nov. Photo: Conrad Hoskin." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8334424/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8334426>
